From 0e0dd739ac60fb9db95be668067d2630a72db71c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: jeeminso <jeeminso@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 19 Sep 2025 16:12:47 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Fix false omission of NULL-assigned sub-columns during
 replica recovery

Ensure null-assigned sub-columns are included in translog entries used
for replica recovery
---
 docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.13.rst     |  3 +
 docs/appendices/release-notes/6.0.3.rst       |  3 +
 .../execution/dml/IndexDocumentBuilder.java   |  8 +--
